{
  "stem": "18450.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You had to go into the city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You didn't have to pay.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the hospital had a place they took you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "To say that it was my mother had gangrene.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They operated on her without anesthesia, because they didn't have any.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't blame them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was the time that the Germans were just pushing more and more.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So whatever they did, I think they did more than-- than anybody would do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] It was-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in the 19-- this was 1941, the end of '41 or the beginning of '42.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was in the beginning of the winter, because the winters there aren't long.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they still have a little of snow, a little of freezing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they have-- the ground is mostly made of-- not-- what they call it-- that you can sink in it, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mud, mostly mud, yellow mud.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, over there, in the winter, you took out the-- the cotton grows on some-- whatever it is there, the-- and you have to take them out.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you use that for-- for wood, to-- to cook with it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what they using, the natives there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They use this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's in the winter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to take out the-- the sticks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if they let you, take a few home and I-- and the rest for them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fine.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
